rkness infusion</a><sup>†</sup>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Gravity Control">gravity control</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Undead Grip">undead grip</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Unnerving Infusion">unnerving infusion</a><sup>†</sup><br /><i>4th</i> - <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Absentia">absentia</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Corpse Puppet">corpse puppet</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Curse Breaker">curse breaker</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Healing Burst">healing burst</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Singularity">singularity</a><sup>†</sup>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Turning Blast">turning blast</a><sup>†</sup><br /><i>5th</i> - <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Eyes of the Void, Greater">eyes of the void, greater</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Gravity Control, Greater">gravity control, greater</a>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Vampiric Infusion">vampiric infusion</a><sup>†</sup><br /><i>6th</i> - <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Darkness Infusion, Greater">darkness infusion, greater</a><sup>†</sup>, <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Suffocate">suffocate</a><br /><i>7th</i> - <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Enervating Infusion">enervating infusion</a><sup>†</sup><br /><i>8th</i> - N/A<br /><i>9th</i> - <a href="KineticistTalentsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Gravity Master">gravity master</a><br /><br /></span>
