            <span id="MainContent_DataListTypes_LabelName_7"><h2 class="title"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Wood</h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy9ujo" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Ultimate Wilderness pg. 58</i></a>, <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy9grw?Pathfinder-Player-Companion-Occult-Origins
